果班仍然最富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地心態冇問題呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為連登班中二病窮撚<br />\n就算自己變唔到富<br />\n都要人地變窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n你地同叫人唔好想打風一樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打風香港仲捱得住<br />\n核戰香港渣都無<br />\n仲有我係對部分連登仔渴望世界大戰既想法表示費解<br />\n到底任何形式既世界大戰對香港 對你地自己有咩好？</blockquote><br />\n你唔想打仗嘅原因好大可能係因為 損害到你自身利益<br />\n點解要從自己利益方面去諗 唔可以太短視 <br />\n戰爭形式唔一定核戰 可以係 貿易戰 非核戰 病毒戰 資訊戰 等等<br />\n合久必分 分久必合 第三次世界大戰係必然嘅事 <br />\n 適當嘅人口滅絕 長遠嚟講對人類文明同地球都係好事 戰爭推動人類科技科學醫學文明進步 解決人口過多問題 資源重新分配 <br />\n死唔去  經過弱肉強食 物競天擇適者生存 生存到最後嘅人 嗰啲先對人類文明進步/進化  有重要嘅影響<br />\nBTW 人類對地球根本有破壞冇建設冇好處 根本唔應該存在<br />\n利申 9upper戴定頭盔"},{"pid":"17777cb5dfb569547a3a4e24bb59d5eb469cf4d3","tid":385214,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"BBC有講過 其實侵想出兵好耐 只係佢個國防部長唔俾......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41105189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41105189&d=yTAR3Yr94ElvWOauvY8tmP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fe1931cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41105189&h=7ccc9375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41105189</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普幾天前才說，他覺得朝鮮最高領導人金正恩「開始尊重」美國，但到了星期三，他發Twitter說：<br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump ✔ @realDonaldTrump<br />\nThe U.S. has been talking to North Korea, and paying them extortion money, for 25 years. Talking is not the answer!<br />\n下午8:47 - 2017年8月30日<br />\n<br />\n「美國一直跟朝鮮對話，也在敲詐之下給他們付錢，都25年了。對話不是答案！」<br />\n其後，馬蒂斯在五角大樓會見宋永武時被記者問到美國是否已經對外交斡旋絶望，馬蒂斯說：「不。我們從來不缺外交對策。」"},{"pid":"b802e614529c04825e48bc6c7daf0b941866db33","tid":385214,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BBC有講過 其實侵想出兵好耐 只係佢個國防部長唔俾......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41105189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41105189&d=yTAR3Yr94ElvWOauvY8tmP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fe1931cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41105189&h=7ccc9375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41105189</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普幾天前才說，他覺得朝鮮最高領導人金正恩「<span style=\"color: red;\">開始尊重</span>」美國，但到了星期三，他發Twitter說：<br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump ✔ @realDonaldTrump<br />\nThe U.S. has been talking to North Korea, and paying them extortion money, for 25 years. Talking is not the answer!<br />\n下午8:47 - 2017年8月30日<br />\n<br />\n「美國一直跟朝鮮對話，也在敲詐之下給他們付錢，都25年了。對話不是答案！」<br />\n其後，馬蒂斯在五角大樓會見宋永武時被記者問到美國是否已經對外交斡旋絶望，馬蒂斯說：「不。我們從來不缺外交對策。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be348c06842860e82d5d8febac8a42857d7e4b","tid":385214,"uid":142965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"10-4-2017"},{"pid":"cf05d2d51eeb43873acc113fed6f45b828e4100d","tid":385214,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb43423c37ecf7232eeb0fbf7f257fbb8e7836bd","tid":385214,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國中國得把口，反而金正恩夠癲，快撚d打</blockquote><br />\n唔知你呢啲人咩心態<br />\n如果你覺得兵荒馬亂，洗牌對你咁有益處既<br />\n你睇下人地敍利亞洗左咁耐牌<br />\n有幾多人貧變富？反而富變貧就一街都係<br />\n仲有最富果班仍然最富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/